    <summary>News extension for creating news with title, image, author, content, published to date. Allow to show on front</summary>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;News extension is integration in one tool all that are need for News publishing:-&#xD;
Title, image, author, content and published on date. &#xD;
Give flexible output (by user defined position) and give link in footer for news list page and can view detail of particular news.&#xD;
User defined position is the best feature of this module. Desire numbers od news items can be positioned in left side and right side. &#xD;
This extension allows add, edit or delete news from the admin panel.&#xD;
&lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;p&gt;Extension easy to install and manage. Install the module, Clear cache and logout, login again to admin panel. Check System-&amp;gt;Configuration, in left side Go to &#x201C;Lavi News&#x201C;, here manage extension options. On front-end view News in left and right position which is enabled in System-&amp;gt;Configuration and also gives a link &amp;quot;News&amp;quot; in the footer. We can enable and disable extension from admin and will decide position on which we want to show news list.&lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&#xD;
